WEBVTT

01:30.830 --> 01:35.030
[Dream of Golden Years]

01:35.770 --> 01:38.520
[2018]

01:36.280 --> 01:37.710
Did you get the movie tickets?

01:37.710 --> 01:38.570
Yeah, got them.

01:38.789 --> 01:40.229
Your favorite—a romance film.

01:40.229 --> 01:40.640
Great.

01:40.870 --> 01:42.130
I even got you popcorn.

01:47.509 --> 01:48.590
Sorry, I'm late.

01:48.720 --> 01:50.050
Why aren't you going in?

01:50.560 --> 01:51.289
Your friend?

01:51.789 --> 01:52.150
No.

01:52.680 --> 01:53.200
Let's go.

01:53.200 --> 01:53.560
Okay.

01:54.200 --> 01:55.509
Here. Happy Valentine's Day.

01:55.509 --> 01:56.110
Thank you.

01:57.039 --> 01:58.440
There are always moments

01:58.509 --> 02:00.370
when everyone else is coupled up,

02:01.200 --> 02:02.430
and I'm all alone.

02:01.310 --> 02:04.090
[Episode 23: Where Is My Happiness?]

02:12.190 --> 02:13.120
How is she doing?

02:13.430 --> 02:14.430
Still in surgery.

02:14.470 --> 02:15.870
Wei went to find out more.

02:19.000 --> 02:19.710
Ms. Xia.

02:20.960 --> 02:21.690
Don't worry.

02:22.079 --> 02:23.310
We're all here for you.

02:23.310 --> 02:23.840
Zhenzhu.

02:25.240 --> 02:26.100
We're all here.

02:31.310 --> 02:32.190
That man

02:32.470 --> 02:33.800
is Li's stepfather.

02:34.190 --> 02:35.910
Li's mother is bedridden due to paralysis.

02:35.910 --> 02:37.870
Her stepfather treats them very badly—

02:37.870 --> 02:39.710
always hitting or scolding them.

02:39.710 --> 02:40.430
So Li

02:40.430 --> 02:41.690
has been saving money,

02:41.710 --> 02:43.570
hoping to take her mother away
from Shengcheng.

02:43.570 --> 02:45.000
She's saved up quite a bit already

02:45.000 --> 02:46.520
and plans to leave next month.

02:46.520 --> 02:47.800
That's also

02:48.150 --> 02:48.840
why she said

02:48.840 --> 02:50.970
she couldn't be Xiaolan's assistant.

02:51.840 --> 02:53.240
How badly is that man hurt?

02:53.240 --> 02:55.079
Li didn't even touch him!

02:55.079 --> 02:56.079
He fell on his own

02:56.079 --> 02:56.540
and then

02:56.560 --> 02:57.360
landed on... uh...

02:57.360 --> 02:58.560
a broken beer bottle.

02:58.840 --> 03:00.400
If you ask me, he got what he deserved!

03:00.400 --> 03:01.660
Should've been worse!

03:01.680 --> 03:03.410
It's good that it wasn't fatal.

03:04.190 --> 03:05.630
With a man like him,

03:05.730 --> 03:06.280
his family

03:06.280 --> 03:07.240
won't be easy to deal with either.

03:07.240 --> 03:08.080
If he had actually died

03:08.080 --> 03:09.120
and his family came to make trouble,

03:09.120 --> 03:11.240
it would only
make things worse for You Li.

03:11.240 --> 03:11.870
True.

03:13.800 --> 03:15.200
Are you You Li's friends?

03:15.800 --> 03:16.150
Yes.

03:16.560 --> 03:17.120
We need to speak with her

03:17.120 --> 03:18.780
to understand the situation.

03:19.280 --> 03:20.480
Please take us to her.

03:21.800 --> 03:22.560
Officers,

03:22.960 --> 03:24.190
You Li is my employee.

03:25.630 --> 03:27.870
Her mother, the only family she has
in Shengcheng,

03:27.870 --> 03:29.800
is still lying in the ICU right now,

03:29.870 --> 03:31.630
hovering between life and death.

03:31.630 --> 03:32.829
Chen Gang downstairs

03:33.030 --> 03:34.470
said you wanted to kill him.

03:34.470 --> 03:35.180
I didn't.

03:35.520 --> 03:36.150
Officers,

03:36.630 --> 03:37.760
I'm You Li's lawyer.

03:38.380 --> 03:39.630
I believe you've already confirmed

03:39.630 --> 03:40.490
with the doctor

03:40.590 --> 03:42.240
that Chen Gang's injury is in his abdomen,

03:42.240 --> 03:43.570
caused by glass shards.

03:43.800 --> 03:45.000
Therefore, his injury

03:45.000 --> 03:45.930
has nothing to do

03:46.079 --> 03:46.800
with You Li.

03:47.790 --> 03:48.630
Then, You Li,

03:49.120 --> 03:50.680
how did Chen Gang fall?

03:55.750 --> 03:57.750
He drank too much and fell on his own.

03:58.600 --> 04:00.200
He gets dead drunk every day.

04:00.310 --> 04:02.440
When he's drunk, he beats my mom and me!

04:02.590 --> 04:03.870
The neighbors all know.

04:03.870 --> 04:05.210
You can go ask them.

04:06.310 --> 04:07.710
When I came back today,

04:08.470 --> 04:11.030
my mom had already been beaten
half to death by him.

04:11.030 --> 04:13.090
Then what made him get violent today?

04:15.280 --> 04:16.000
Because he found out

04:16.000 --> 04:17.529
I wanted to take my mom away.

04:18.120 --> 04:19.720
I wanted to get away from him.

04:20.000 --> 04:21.310
If I stayed any longer,

04:21.800 --> 04:22.270
he would've beaten

04:22.270 --> 04:23.930
both my mother and me to death!

04:24.120 --> 04:24.830
Officers,

04:25.580 --> 04:27.160
You Li had a promotion within reach.

04:27.160 --> 04:28.750
She gave it up precisely because she

04:28.750 --> 04:30.480
needed to take her mother away.

04:30.520 --> 04:32.190
Who would throw away
such a good opportunity

04:32.190 --> 04:34.650
unless they had
absolutely no other choice?

04:36.000 --> 04:36.460
Listen,

04:37.070 --> 04:38.930
your mother needs care right now.

04:39.150 --> 04:41.040
Don't leave Shengcheng for the time being.

04:41.040 --> 04:42.360
We need to be able to find you at any time

04:42.360 --> 04:44.020
to understand the situation.

04:44.159 --> 04:44.800
What about Chen Gang

04:44.800 --> 04:45.930
beating her mother?

04:46.310 --> 04:47.000
Officers!

04:48.510 --> 04:49.390
I was there too.

04:49.560 --> 04:50.240
If there's anything you need to know,

04:50.240 --> 04:51.040
you can ask me.

04:51.100 --> 04:51.680
That bastard

04:51.680 --> 04:53.120
hit her mother in the head with a stick.

04:53.120 --> 04:54.560
And her mother couldn't even move.

04:54.560 --> 04:55.420
Attorney Zhou,

04:55.430 --> 04:57.560
would that count as attempted murder?

04:58.270 --> 04:59.480
Officers, I believe

04:59.920 --> 05:01.720
you'll make the right judgment.

05:01.750 --> 05:02.480
Don't worry.

05:03.570 --> 05:04.310
We will continue

05:04.310 --> 05:05.870
our investigation into Chen Gang.

05:05.870 --> 05:07.120
Take good care of your mother.

05:07.120 --> 05:08.180
We'll be going now.

05:08.310 --> 05:08.840
Let's go.

05:09.040 --> 05:09.390
Thank you.

05:09.390 --> 05:09.990
Thank you.

05:14.940 --> 05:15.830
What are you doing?

05:15.830 --> 05:16.230
Get up.

05:18.870 --> 05:19.560
Thank you.

05:21.440 --> 05:22.270
Thank you all.

05:24.070 --> 05:25.400
Go check on your mother.

05:33.780 --> 05:35.580
The patient is out of danger now,

05:35.650 --> 05:37.630
but I can't say for sure

05:37.920 --> 05:39.250
whether she'll wake up.

05:39.600 --> 05:41.800
The patient has been paralyzed for years,

05:41.800 --> 05:43.710
and this time the trauma was severe.

05:43.710 --> 05:44.390
Aside from standard

05:44.390 --> 05:45.520
medical treatment,

05:45.980 --> 05:47.270
your support as family members

05:47.270 --> 05:48.120
and the patient's

05:48.120 --> 05:49.180
own will to survive

05:49.270 --> 05:50.430
are both very important.

05:50.430 --> 05:52.030
Please take good care of her.

05:52.220 --> 05:53.100
It's my job.

05:53.510 --> 05:54.840
-Thank you.
-Thank you.

06:02.920 --> 06:03.320
You Li,

06:04.310 --> 06:05.040
don't worry.

06:05.680 --> 06:07.160
If there's any update from the police,

06:07.160 --> 06:08.480
they'll contact me first.

06:08.480 --> 06:10.040
Just focus on taking care of your mom.

06:10.040 --> 06:10.800
If you need anything,

06:10.800 --> 06:11.460
just say it.

06:11.850 --> 06:13.000
We have plenty of hands at the shop—

06:13.000 --> 06:14.000
we can all help out.

06:14.000 --> 06:14.400
Right.

06:14.560 --> 06:16.830
Don't hesitate to ask
our Sis Bai for help.

06:16.830 --> 06:17.310
Li,

06:18.310 --> 06:19.000
you must want

06:19.000 --> 06:20.260
your mother to wake up,

06:20.310 --> 06:20.750
right?

06:22.560 --> 06:23.510
Then you should let her

06:23.510 --> 06:25.630
receive proper treatment here
in the hospital.

06:25.630 --> 06:27.430
Don't worry about the expenses.

06:27.630 --> 06:29.560
The company will cover it upfront.

06:29.830 --> 06:30.560
Ms. Xia,

06:31.040 --> 06:33.440
I know how costly medical treatment
can be.

06:33.720 --> 06:34.780
This is too much...

06:35.120 --> 06:36.070
I said,

06:36.680 --> 06:38.000
we'll only cover it upfront.

06:38.000 --> 06:39.310
Don't feel burdened by it.

06:39.310 --> 06:41.370
Think of it as a loan from the company.

06:41.870 --> 06:43.000
From now on, I'll deduct

06:43.000 --> 06:44.120
part of your salary each month

06:44.120 --> 06:45.159
as repayment.

06:45.600 --> 06:46.330
Is that okay?

06:47.159 --> 06:47.600
Okay.

06:48.800 --> 06:49.860
Thank you, Ms. Xia.

06:50.630 --> 06:51.830
For the next few days,

06:51.920 --> 06:53.130
stay here

06:53.159 --> 06:54.760
and take care of your mother.

06:54.800 --> 06:56.260
When she gets a bit better,

06:56.680 --> 06:58.540
you can come back to work anytime.

07:00.270 --> 07:01.390
Come back to work?

07:03.070 --> 07:03.750
Ms. Xia...

07:05.160 --> 07:05.830
you still want me

07:05.830 --> 07:07.030
to be your assistant?

07:08.160 --> 07:08.760
Of course.

07:09.390 --> 07:10.560
You've always been my top choice

07:10.560 --> 07:11.560
for an assistant.

07:12.680 --> 07:13.190
Li,

07:13.830 --> 07:15.160
I really believe in you.

07:16.040 --> 07:16.770
You are smart

07:17.160 --> 07:17.920
and capable.

07:18.270 --> 07:18.920
Why shouldn't you

07:18.920 --> 07:20.160
have a better job

07:20.800 --> 07:22.060
and a brighter future?

07:27.190 --> 07:27.800
Ms. Xia...

07:29.870 --> 07:30.480
thank you.

07:32.470 --> 07:33.270
It's nothing.

07:40.270 --> 07:41.730
Shengcheng's city lights

07:41.920 --> 07:43.380
get brighter every night.

07:43.630 --> 07:44.159
Yes.

07:44.800 --> 07:46.460
There used to be nothing here.

07:46.950 --> 07:48.680
Now it's home to so many people.

07:49.270 --> 07:50.600
My mother used to think

07:51.120 --> 07:52.920
that only our hometown was home.

07:53.310 --> 07:55.710
She doesn't think that way anymore either.

07:56.900 --> 07:58.960
When you're with the people you love,

07:59.070 --> 08:00.670
anywhere can feel like home.

08:03.510 --> 08:04.310
You know what?

08:04.830 --> 08:06.780
Li today reminded me of

08:06.810 --> 08:08.870
when I first woke up in the Xia family.

08:09.480 --> 08:11.790
Only when you've been pushed
to the very edge

08:11.790 --> 08:14.390
do you find the strength
to fight for your life.

08:17.630 --> 08:18.360
Li...

08:19.430 --> 08:20.430
is a brave girl.

08:21.510 --> 08:22.480
She deserves

08:23.240 --> 08:24.190
a better life.

08:26.720 --> 08:27.310
Yeah.

08:27.920 --> 08:29.120
But I know how hard

08:29.120 --> 08:29.920
that path is.

08:30.680 --> 08:31.340
Zhou Cheng,

08:32.390 --> 08:33.200
tell me,

08:33.200 --> 08:34.530
why do we try our hardest

08:35.360 --> 08:36.360
yet still

08:37.030 --> 08:38.559
can't find more happiness?

08:41.030 --> 08:43.090
Because once you set out on this road,

08:43.720 --> 08:44.920
there's no stopping.

08:46.510 --> 08:48.240
Life was never meant to be easy.

08:48.910 --> 08:49.480
So naturally,

08:49.480 --> 08:51.810
there isn't all that much happiness in it.

08:52.150 --> 08:53.280
But because of that,

08:54.030 --> 08:55.240
those fleeting

08:55.240 --> 08:56.440
moments of happiness

08:56.480 --> 08:57.940
are all the more precious.

09:00.630 --> 09:01.240
Yeah.

09:02.750 --> 09:04.480
I know I shouldn't be so greedy.

09:05.440 --> 09:06.300
But Zhou Cheng,

09:07.080 --> 09:08.200
I still hope

09:08.870 --> 09:10.670
there can be more happy moments—

09:11.840 --> 09:12.390
for you,

09:12.910 --> 09:13.390
me,

09:14.000 --> 09:14.800
and everyone.

09:16.030 --> 09:16.630
Oh, right,

09:17.150 --> 09:18.600
Du Zhaohui mentioned

09:18.840 --> 09:21.120
-that he found Granny Yu's antiques...
-Xiaolan.

09:21.120 --> 09:22.550
You already had a long day.

09:22.550 --> 09:23.680
Let's not talk about

09:23.720 --> 09:24.920
anything else today,

09:25.240 --> 09:25.670
okay?

09:45.510 --> 09:46.600
Have you noted down

09:46.600 --> 09:47.490
all the adjustments needed?

09:47.490 --> 09:47.970
Got it.

09:48.000 --> 09:48.870
During construction,

09:48.870 --> 09:50.000
safety comes first.

09:50.080 --> 09:50.720
-Got it.
-Yes.

09:50.720 --> 09:52.050
Alright, go get to work.

09:52.390 --> 09:52.850
Ms. Xia!

09:53.670 --> 09:55.030
We've arranged a place for You Li.

09:55.030 --> 09:56.600
It's close to
both the hospital and the company.

09:56.600 --> 09:57.550
I stopped by the hospital earlier

09:57.550 --> 09:58.910
and dropped off the keys.

09:58.910 --> 09:59.910
How is her mother?

10:00.200 --> 10:01.120
She hasn't woken up yet.

10:01.120 --> 10:01.750
But her condition

10:01.750 --> 10:03.350
is better than two weeks ago.

10:03.720 --> 10:05.630
Li plans to hire a daytime caregiver.

10:05.630 --> 10:07.030
She wants to come back to work.

10:07.030 --> 10:07.440
Okay.

10:07.670 --> 10:09.080
Then help her get familiar

10:09.080 --> 10:09.790
with the company's operations first.

10:09.790 --> 10:10.150
Okay.

10:12.200 --> 10:12.730
Xiaolan,

10:13.270 --> 10:13.870
come here.

10:14.080 --> 10:14.720
Mr. Mao.

10:17.750 --> 10:20.550
You're always telling others
to stay on top of their work,

10:20.550 --> 10:21.790
but I think you're letting

10:21.790 --> 10:22.750
your own slide.

10:23.840 --> 10:25.200
You talk a big game—

10:25.480 --> 10:26.870
learn from my experience

10:26.870 --> 10:28.150
and get some hands-on practice.

10:28.150 --> 10:29.200
But what happened?

10:29.200 --> 10:30.320
You just leave the construction site to me

10:30.320 --> 10:31.320
and run off.

10:31.840 --> 10:33.770
You're not even as attentive as Du.

10:35.440 --> 10:36.200
Du?

10:37.240 --> 10:39.270
Du's been here every day
supervising the site.

10:39.270 --> 10:40.390
Xiaolan, listen—

10:40.980 --> 10:42.550
you really need to learn from Du

10:42.550 --> 10:43.310
on this.

10:43.840 --> 10:45.100
Architectural design

10:45.440 --> 10:47.670
isn't just about finishing drawings.

10:48.080 --> 10:50.010
You need to follow through
with the project's progress.

10:50.010 --> 10:51.400
Only then can you spot

10:51.550 --> 10:52.360
problems

10:52.390 --> 10:53.320
in your designs

10:53.630 --> 10:55.270
and improve them later.

10:56.270 --> 10:56.720
Yes.

10:56.910 --> 10:58.170
You're right, Mr. Mao.

10:58.480 --> 10:58.960
Mr. Mao,

10:59.240 --> 11:00.240
if the lecture is over,

11:00.240 --> 11:01.360
can you let me

11:01.510 --> 11:02.910
have Ms. Xia for a moment?

11:04.320 --> 11:05.580
Alright, you two talk.

11:07.550 --> 11:08.390
Du, Du?

11:08.790 --> 11:10.250
I've sold my house and car.

11:10.440 --> 11:11.670
Now, I'm just plain Du,
not a young master anymore.

11:11.670 --> 11:14.000
You have to take responsibility for that.

11:14.150 --> 11:16.360
I'll be responsible for your investment.

11:16.360 --> 11:18.620
The electronics industry is the future.

11:19.000 --> 11:21.400
Building an electronics mall
is a sure win.

11:21.600 --> 11:22.670
Yeah, yeah.

11:23.600 --> 11:25.240
As for the antiques you asked me to find,

11:25.240 --> 11:26.440
I've put the word out.

11:26.770 --> 11:28.810
A few similar pieces

11:28.840 --> 11:30.360
have appeared in antique shops recently.

11:30.360 --> 11:32.560
Some details match what you described,

11:32.600 --> 11:33.750
but I need more information

11:33.750 --> 11:35.410
to compare them more clearly.

11:35.960 --> 11:37.200
Is there any way

11:37.510 --> 11:38.570
to get some photos?

11:38.790 --> 11:39.910
The Yu family sold

11:40.120 --> 11:41.450
quite a lot of antiques.

11:41.550 --> 11:42.720
Granny Yu can't remember

11:42.720 --> 11:44.450
the specific details clearly.

11:44.480 --> 11:45.510
But if there were photos,

11:45.510 --> 11:46.960
she'd definitely remember.

11:46.960 --> 11:47.320
Okay.

11:47.510 --> 11:48.770
I'll ask around again.

11:49.480 --> 11:52.440
If I manage to get the photos,

11:52.720 --> 11:53.510
I wonder if you

11:53.510 --> 11:54.710
might do me the honor.

11:58.960 --> 11:59.720
You know

12:00.000 --> 12:01.600
that resort by Qingyue Lake?

12:02.440 --> 12:04.200
The one the Americans built?

12:04.380 --> 12:04.690
Yes.

12:04.720 --> 12:06.030
I read in the newspaper

12:06.120 --> 12:07.450
that it's opening soon.

12:07.600 --> 12:08.390
So,

12:08.720 --> 12:10.080
would you do me the honor

12:10.120 --> 12:12.520
of attending the resort's opening with me?

12:14.670 --> 12:15.130
I can't.

12:15.720 --> 12:16.920
I already have plans.

12:49.620 --> 12:51.000
My leg is broken! My leg is broken!

12:51.000 --> 12:51.550
My leg!

12:51.960 --> 12:53.290
You have to pay for this!

12:56.030 --> 12:57.760
You did that on purpose, right?

12:57.960 --> 12:59.030
Do you know

12:59.030 --> 12:59.910
what that behavior of yours is called?

12:59.910 --> 13:00.840
Staging a crash.

13:02.000 --> 13:02.860
Staging a what?

13:04.390 --> 13:05.250
Meaning a scam.

13:05.600 --> 13:06.320
Scam?

13:06.600 --> 13:06.960
I...

13:07.870 --> 13:08.280
Well,

13:08.440 --> 13:09.510
you made me take a huge fall.

13:09.510 --> 13:10.270
S-Shouldn't you

13:10.270 --> 13:11.150
compensate me somehow?

13:11.150 --> 13:13.010
A-And you said I s-staged a crash?

13:13.150 --> 13:14.280
Did I crash into you?

13:14.670 --> 13:16.270
Where did I crash into you? Tell me!

13:16.270 --> 13:16.870
Did I crash into you?

13:16.870 --> 13:18.030
When did I ever crash into you?

13:18.030 --> 13:18.390
I...

13:19.200 --> 13:19.600
I...

13:20.870 --> 13:21.200
I...

13:21.480 --> 13:22.410
What do you want?

13:23.750 --> 13:25.030
It's alright. Ignore him.

13:25.030 --> 13:26.270
He's just a sleazy thug.

13:26.270 --> 13:27.320
Hey, who are you calling a sleazy thug?

13:27.320 --> 13:28.200
-You.
-You.

13:29.390 --> 13:30.480
This is not over!

13:34.910 --> 13:36.030
Are you okay, Xiaolan?

13:36.030 --> 13:36.560
I'm fine.

13:40.840 --> 13:41.550
It's quite cold.

13:41.550 --> 13:42.390
You want to try that?

13:42.390 --> 13:43.250
Yeah, that one.

13:46.000 --> 13:47.320
That one looks fun too.

13:47.670 --> 13:48.800
Let's go take a look.

13:57.440 --> 13:58.170
How did it go?

13:58.910 --> 14:01.040
Everything is arranged. Don't worry.

14:08.840 --> 14:09.370
Yaozong.

14:11.720 --> 14:13.000
Why is it just you two?
Where are the others?

14:13.000 --> 14:14.240
They will be here any minute!

14:14.240 --> 14:14.550
I...

14:15.260 --> 14:15.840
T-Then, Jie,

14:15.840 --> 14:16.390
you wait here.

14:16.390 --> 14:17.200
When everyone's here, catch up with us!

14:17.200 --> 14:17.730
Let's go.

14:30.350 --> 14:31.830
You bitch! You kicked me?

14:31.910 --> 14:33.640
I'll kill you in a minute. Move!

14:39.870 --> 14:40.530
Who are you?

14:41.440 --> 14:42.370
What do you want?

14:43.240 --> 14:43.840
I want her.

14:44.750 --> 14:46.060
Are you trying to bully her?

14:46.060 --> 14:47.660
Hey, mind your own business.

14:54.390 --> 14:55.910
This is a law-governed society,
I'm telling you.

14:55.910 --> 14:56.870
My dad is the village chief.

14:56.870 --> 14:58.030
If you lay a hand on me,
none of you will get away.

14:58.030 --> 14:58.870
Believe it or not, I'll make sure

14:58.870 --> 15:00.130
you never make it back!

15:00.240 --> 15:01.750
Make sure I never make it back?

15:01.750 --> 15:02.120
I...

15:11.840 --> 15:12.720
Nobody move!

15:12.750 --> 15:13.790
Surround them!

15:16.550 --> 15:17.950
What are you waiting for?

15:18.510 --> 15:19.870
The loser ends up in the hospital;

15:19.870 --> 15:21.110
the winner ends up in court.

15:21.110 --> 15:23.000
Either way, nobody comes out ahead.

15:23.000 --> 15:24.130
Still want to fight?

15:25.150 --> 15:25.680
Yaozong.

15:26.630 --> 15:27.790
Maybe we should just let it go.

15:27.790 --> 15:28.790
It's not worth it.

15:28.960 --> 15:29.960
They have knives.

15:31.080 --> 15:31.480
Okay.

15:34.080 --> 15:35.080
I... I'm in a good mood today.

15:35.080 --> 15:37.010
I'll let you off the hook this time.

15:38.080 --> 15:39.540
Still trying to act tough?

15:40.630 --> 15:41.690
Get out of here now!

15:41.790 --> 15:43.650
I.. Go, go, go! Hurry up! Let's go!

15:47.390 --> 15:49.320
Alright, everyone, get in the car!

15:49.480 --> 15:50.030
Xiaolan,

15:50.550 --> 15:52.150
page me if you need anything!

15:52.200 --> 15:53.390
I'm off now!

15:53.670 --> 15:54.870
Okay, thanks, Uncle!

15:55.270 --> 15:56.330
Drive safe, Uncle!

15:59.320 --> 15:59.780
Sis Bai,

16:00.200 --> 16:00.600
San,

16:00.750 --> 16:01.200
Wei,

16:01.510 --> 16:02.310
thank you all.

16:02.750 --> 16:03.480
No problem.

16:03.480 --> 16:04.360
Don't mention it.

16:04.360 --> 16:05.360
We're all family.

16:05.890 --> 16:06.200
By the way,

16:06.200 --> 16:07.200
when I came over just now,

16:07.200 --> 16:07.670
I noticed a place over there—

16:07.670 --> 16:08.720
it's huge and looks really fun.

16:08.720 --> 16:09.320
Let's take a break

16:09.320 --> 16:10.790
and have some fun together?

16:10.790 --> 16:11.450
We'll pass.

16:11.560 --> 16:12.910
We'll just walk around nearby.

16:12.910 --> 16:13.870
We've got something else to attend to.

16:13.870 --> 16:14.550
You guys have fun.

16:14.550 --> 16:15.720
You've got other business.

16:15.720 --> 16:16.600
Come on, here!

16:17.000 --> 16:17.440
Cheng,

16:17.910 --> 16:19.170
protect Xiaolan well.

16:19.750 --> 16:20.750
Come on, let's go.

16:20.840 --> 16:21.440
We're off!

16:21.510 --> 16:21.870
Bye!

16:22.120 --> 16:22.650
Bye-bye!

16:22.790 --> 16:23.670
It'll definitely be fun.

16:23.670 --> 16:24.630
Where is the place?

16:24.630 --> 16:26.290
What? Is there a Ferris wheel?

16:33.370 --> 16:34.480
The way you play with the knife

16:34.480 --> 16:35.880
reminds me of Peter Chan.

16:36.790 --> 16:37.510
Who is he?

16:39.630 --> 16:40.430
From Gangdao.

16:41.120 --> 16:42.030
From Gangdao?

16:42.670 --> 16:43.730
Never heard of him.

16:45.270 --> 16:47.000
You'll hear about him someday.

16:49.000 --> 16:49.670
Mr. Zhou,

16:50.510 --> 16:51.320
you had a reason

16:51.320 --> 16:52.140
for bringing me out here, didn't you?

16:52.140 --> 16:54.340
It can't just be a casual stroll, right?

16:54.630 --> 16:55.960
You said it was a day out,

16:56.120 --> 16:58.250
but really it's a site visit, isn't it?

16:58.270 --> 16:58.750
Ms. Xia,

16:59.390 --> 17:00.240
the Americans

17:00.240 --> 17:01.360
built a resort here

17:01.600 --> 17:02.750
and a golf course.

17:03.030 --> 17:04.440
That clearly means

17:04.440 --> 17:05.480
the project's location is excellent.

17:05.480 --> 17:08.740
So wouldn't it also be suitable
for property development?

17:09.440 --> 17:10.640
Since you put it that way, Mr. Zhou,

17:10.640 --> 17:12.700
have you already picked a spot for me?

17:13.400 --> 17:14.790
When I came out earlier to make a call

17:14.790 --> 17:15.849
and passed by here,

17:16.030 --> 17:17.089
it suddenly hit me.

17:18.200 --> 17:18.589
Look.

18:08.440 --> 18:10.270
You're staring at this stinking ditch,

18:10.270 --> 18:11.200
practically drooling over it—

18:11.200 --> 18:13.160
it's really weird.

18:14.300 --> 18:15.550
Didn't you bring me here

18:15.550 --> 18:17.160
just to check this plot of land?

18:17.160 --> 18:18.490
Didn't someone once say

18:18.680 --> 18:20.940
the three principles of real estate are:

18:21.110 --> 18:24.510
-location, location, location?
-Location, location, location.

18:24.510 --> 18:26.770
This place looks messy and run-down now,

18:27.110 --> 18:28.710
but its geographic position

18:28.750 --> 18:29.720
is exceptional.

18:30.680 --> 18:33.110
This side is the Qingyue Lake Resort,

18:33.480 --> 18:34.680
and on the other side is the golf course

18:34.680 --> 18:36.810
that the Americans are about to build.

18:36.830 --> 18:38.420
It sits right between the two—

18:38.420 --> 18:39.400
just like the pearl

18:39.400 --> 18:42.400
in the classic motif
where two dragons chase after it.

18:42.830 --> 18:43.510
Mr. Zhou,

18:43.750 --> 18:44.810
you have a good eye.

18:45.880 --> 18:47.610
But there's still one problem.

18:47.680 --> 18:49.640
This plot sits right
between the two pieces of land

18:49.640 --> 18:50.840
the Americans chose.

18:50.960 --> 18:51.880
So why was this particular piece

18:51.880 --> 18:52.750
left out?

18:53.240 --> 18:54.250
Just because

18:54.310 --> 18:55.570
it's a stinking ditch?

18:56.370 --> 18:57.300
That can't be it.

18:57.550 --> 18:58.920
No developer

18:58.920 --> 19:00.310
would pass up a plot

19:00.400 --> 19:01.270
with such a prime location

19:01.270 --> 19:02.920
for something superficial like that.

19:02.920 --> 19:04.480
There must be other underlying issues.

19:04.480 --> 19:06.610
I'll go back and have them look into it.

19:08.270 --> 19:10.000
I didn't bring my cell phone.

19:10.310 --> 19:12.440
I need to contact Ge Jian immediately.

19:13.830 --> 19:15.750
Ms. Xia, you really
make every second count.

19:15.750 --> 19:16.310
Of course,

19:16.310 --> 19:17.510
time waits for no one!

19:18.960 --> 19:20.350
That piece of land

19:20.550 --> 19:22.510
should be about 20 mu.

19:22.920 --> 19:25.030
Based on the price the Americans paid,

19:25.030 --> 19:27.400
it's about 150,000 per mu.

19:27.960 --> 19:28.640
That means

19:28.640 --> 19:30.520
if we can come up with three million,

19:30.520 --> 19:31.980
we should be able to get it.

19:33.640 --> 19:34.960
The dividends from

19:34.980 --> 19:36.400
the materials center and Luna

19:36.400 --> 19:38.350
for this quarter should be 1.5 million.

19:38.350 --> 19:40.110
Plus the money I've saved up,

19:40.110 --> 19:42.110
and Du Zhaohui's consulting fee...

19:45.310 --> 19:46.790
As for Du Zhaohui,

19:47.030 --> 19:48.920
better not count on anything from him

19:48.920 --> 19:50.410
before his Electronics City opens.

19:50.410 --> 19:51.240
Uncle might

19:51.270 --> 19:52.030
still be able to

19:52.030 --> 19:53.430
free up some funds for me.

19:53.920 --> 19:55.380
All things considered...

19:56.590 --> 19:57.990
we might be able to get it.

19:59.410 --> 20:02.040
Although the exact price and acreage

20:02.070 --> 20:04.070
will need to be officially assessed
by the government,

20:04.070 --> 20:05.110
it won't vary by more than

20:05.110 --> 20:06.000
100,000.

20:06.720 --> 20:08.520
So it really should be feasible.

20:10.270 --> 20:11.800
After saving up for so long,

20:12.310 --> 20:14.510
I finally have enough to get in the game.

20:15.160 --> 20:17.020
So, we have the money for the land.

20:17.270 --> 20:19.470
What about the money for construction?

20:19.590 --> 20:21.000
For construction...

20:21.550 --> 20:23.270
we'll have to take a bit of a risk.

20:23.270 --> 20:25.310
What... kind of risk?

20:27.240 --> 20:28.440
We'll take out loans.

20:28.830 --> 20:29.440
Step one:

20:29.830 --> 20:31.200
take out a mortgage loan.

20:31.200 --> 20:32.070
Once we have the land,

20:32.070 --> 20:33.000
we can mortgage it

20:33.000 --> 20:34.270
to the bank for a loan.

20:34.550 --> 20:35.400
That money

20:35.400 --> 20:36.550
will serve as

20:36.550 --> 20:37.720
our initial capital

20:37.750 --> 20:39.110
to begin construction.

20:39.440 --> 20:40.000
Step two:

20:40.240 --> 20:41.240
sell off-plan.

20:41.440 --> 20:43.270
Reserve your off-plan apartment—
delivery in a year!

20:43.270 --> 20:44.160
Starting now!

20:44.200 --> 20:45.510
-I want one!
-I want one!

20:45.510 --> 20:47.200
After the bank loan comes through,

20:47.200 --> 20:49.200
we can build a model building first.

20:49.240 --> 20:50.850
With that as a reference,

20:50.880 --> 20:52.370
we can start pre-sales.

20:52.400 --> 20:54.460
Which is what people
from Gangdao often do:

20:54.460 --> 20:55.660
sell off-plan apartments.

20:55.660 --> 20:56.880
The deposits from the first buyers

20:56.880 --> 20:58.960
can then fund
the construction of the next building.

20:58.960 --> 21:01.120
That does sound feasible.

21:01.830 --> 21:03.080
But every sum of money

21:03.110 --> 21:04.510
has to line up perfectly.

21:05.030 --> 21:06.920
If there's even a slight glitch

21:07.070 --> 21:09.000
or a delay in funds coming through,

21:09.000 --> 21:11.600
the entire cash flow
could break at any moment.

21:11.920 --> 21:13.310
It is indeed a bit risky.

21:13.680 --> 21:15.110
But a location this good

21:15.270 --> 21:16.670
is really hard to come by.

21:16.960 --> 21:18.440
If I give up now,

21:18.880 --> 21:19.790
I'm afraid

21:19.790 --> 21:21.000
that every time I pass by there,

21:21.000 --> 21:21.860
I'll regret it.

21:22.960 --> 21:25.290
Ever since I chose to study architecture,

21:25.350 --> 21:27.280
I've been waiting for this moment.

21:27.480 --> 21:28.880
So I don't want to give up.

21:29.350 --> 21:30.550
I want to give it a try.

21:31.440 --> 21:31.770
Okay.

21:32.920 --> 21:34.180
Since you've decided,

21:34.750 --> 21:36.080
I'm with you all the way.

21:38.110 --> 21:39.170
More importantly,

21:39.480 --> 21:40.540
I really don't know

21:40.960 --> 21:42.680
how much time I have left.

21:45.760 --> 21:46.560
But, Xiaolan,

21:47.240 --> 21:48.640
most housing nowadays

21:48.640 --> 21:50.750
is still allocated by work units.

21:51.510 --> 21:52.200
Very few people

21:52.200 --> 21:53.680
actually buy commercial housing,

21:53.680 --> 21:54.640
let alone

21:54.720 --> 21:55.960
buy something they can't even see yet—

21:55.960 --> 21:57.290
just a promise on paper.

21:57.680 --> 21:59.110
I feel like this is

21:59.510 --> 22:00.200
just like

22:00.200 --> 22:01.260
that resort hotel—

22:01.270 --> 22:02.310
only a very small number of people

22:02.310 --> 22:03.110
can afford it.

22:03.640 --> 22:04.200
So,

22:04.550 --> 22:05.920
our target customers are

22:05.920 --> 22:07.680
the Gangdao businesspeople
who have come to

22:07.680 --> 22:09.510
Shengcheng for business
and are already familiar

22:09.510 --> 22:11.570
with the off-plan property concept.

22:12.830 --> 22:14.760
The hard part isn't buying the land

22:14.830 --> 22:16.000
but getting the apartments sold.

22:16.000 --> 22:18.330
People from Gangdao care a lot about luck.

22:18.480 --> 22:19.070
The news

22:19.070 --> 22:21.070
that the Americans passed on this plot

22:21.070 --> 22:22.670
will get out sooner or later.

22:23.040 --> 22:25.320
We need a good story

22:25.350 --> 22:26.920
to reshape how buyers

22:27.270 --> 22:28.880
see the smelly ditch.

22:30.000 --> 22:31.730
I can figure all that out later.

22:32.070 --> 22:32.850
Right now, I need to think about

22:32.850 --> 22:34.450
what other steps are needed.

22:39.720 --> 22:41.240
Is it about the hospital?

22:42.510 --> 22:43.640
It's okay. Go ahead.

22:45.720 --> 22:46.160
Okay.

22:47.830 --> 22:48.360
Bye-bye.

23:01.240 --> 23:03.500
After dreaming about this for so long...

23:04.550 --> 23:06.150
can I finally make it happen?

23:07.510 --> 23:08.120
Ms. Xia,

23:08.480 --> 23:09.750
it's not impossible for you

23:09.750 --> 23:10.750
to purchase land.

23:11.160 --> 23:11.830
There's already a precedent—

23:11.830 --> 23:13.000
as recently as last year,

23:13.000 --> 23:14.350
a private company acquired land.

23:14.350 --> 23:15.270
That's wonderful.

23:15.270 --> 23:16.680
What paperwork do I need?

23:17.110 --> 23:17.640
First,

23:17.880 --> 23:19.030
you need to register

23:19.350 --> 23:20.610
a real estate company.

23:21.160 --> 23:22.290
Qihang Real Estate.

23:22.510 --> 23:23.350
Qihang, as in

23:23.740 --> 23:24.160
setting sail and traveling far.

23:23.860 --> 23:26.020
[Business License;
Legal Representative: Xia Xiaolan]

23:24.160 --> 23:24.590
Then,

23:24.800 --> 23:25.960
you'll also need to affiliate with

23:25.960 --> 23:27.790
a state-owned enterprise
with construction qualifications.

23:27.790 --> 23:28.240
This

23:28.400 --> 23:29.750
is the most important step.

23:29.750 --> 23:31.720
Longcheng No. 2 Construction Group?

23:31.720 --> 23:32.830
That would be perfect.

23:32.830 --> 23:35.030
I have a former student working there.

23:35.110 --> 23:36.070
I'll reach out to him first for you.

23:36.070 --> 23:36.440
Okay.

23:36.720 --> 23:37.780
Thank you, Mr. Mao.

23:38.550 --> 23:39.080
Finally,

23:39.240 --> 23:40.480
you need to prepare

23:40.510 --> 23:42.070
a letter of intent for land lease,

23:42.070 --> 23:43.270
detailing the proposed planning

23:43.270 --> 23:44.200
and purpose of the land.

23:44.200 --> 23:45.160
Any content relating to waste management

23:45.160 --> 23:46.480
and improving the city's appearance

23:46.480 --> 23:47.160
can be emphasized

23:47.160 --> 23:48.220
and expanded upon.

23:49.430 --> 23:50.000
[Letter of Intent to Lease Land]

23:49.640 --> 23:50.100
Ms. Xia,

23:50.680 --> 23:52.360
I went to inquire about it
a couple of days ago.

23:52.360 --> 23:53.480
The subdistrict office sent people

23:53.480 --> 23:54.740
to remeasure the plot.

23:54.750 --> 23:55.610
It's over 20 mu.

23:55.790 --> 23:57.640
Turns out the chief of Ganquan Village

23:57.640 --> 23:58.880
had tampered with the records

23:58.880 --> 23:59.750
during the government's

23:59.750 --> 24:00.810
land acquisition.

24:01.200 --> 24:02.800
It wasn't that the Americans

24:02.960 --> 24:04.000
didn't want this plot;

24:04.000 --> 24:05.860
they just didn't know it existed.

24:10.070 --> 24:11.400
Is he genuinely ignorant of the law,

24:11.400 --> 24:13.200
or is he up to something crooked?

24:13.640 --> 24:14.730
Look into it further.

24:14.730 --> 24:15.790
Even though we can just

24:15.790 --> 24:17.160
apply to the government
to acquire the land

24:17.160 --> 24:18.440
and follow the procedure,

24:18.440 --> 24:19.440
I don't want there to be

24:19.440 --> 24:20.720
any hidden trouble later on.

24:20.720 --> 24:21.920
Understood, Ms. Xia.

24:27.770 --> 24:29.450
Who parked this car on my road?

24:29.920 --> 24:31.000
Sorry, it's ours.

24:31.030 --> 24:31.920
We'll leave in a bit.

24:31.920 --> 24:32.870
Leave now!

24:33.750 --> 24:34.880
Drive it away now!

24:35.400 --> 24:36.140
Drive...

24:37.400 --> 24:38.400
Ouch, ouch, ouch!

24:39.480 --> 24:40.830
Hey, you... Don't go!

24:41.560 --> 24:42.680
I'm telling you, this is not over.

24:42.680 --> 24:43.610
You just said...

24:44.110 --> 24:45.110
this is your road?

24:46.750 --> 24:47.120
I...

24:47.160 --> 24:48.160
Stop right there!

24:49.030 --> 24:50.090
Last time, you said

24:50.290 --> 24:52.350
your dad is the village chief, right?

24:52.590 --> 24:55.090
I was just taking a shortcut home.

24:55.870 --> 24:57.350
That woman with the knife
isn't around, right?

24:57.350 --> 24:58.150
That woman...

24:58.200 --> 25:00.030
I've turned over a new leaf now.

25:00.070 --> 25:00.790
I haven't set foot

25:00.790 --> 25:01.830
near Qingyue Lake in ages!

25:01.830 --> 25:02.630
Stop yelling.

25:02.920 --> 25:04.120
Answer my questions.

25:06.830 --> 25:08.760
It's the chief! My dad is the chief!

25:09.880 --> 25:10.410
Alright.

25:11.200 --> 25:12.730
I won't beat you today then.

25:13.000 --> 25:14.240
Go back and ask your dad

25:14.240 --> 25:15.790
why he concealed
and didn't report this plot

25:15.790 --> 25:17.450
during the land acquisition.

25:17.680 --> 25:18.350
Get a clear answer,

25:18.350 --> 25:20.270
then wait for me here tomorrow morning.

25:20.270 --> 25:21.750
Don't get any funny ideas.

25:22.350 --> 25:24.030
Or else that woman with the knife

25:24.030 --> 25:25.350
might show up anytime.

25:25.720 --> 25:26.450
Okay, ma'am.

25:27.590 --> 25:28.120
Goodbye.

25:32.400 --> 25:32.960
Ms. Xia,

25:33.550 --> 25:36.010
can a guy like that
actually get things done?

25:36.210 --> 25:37.160
It doesn't matter.

25:37.160 --> 25:38.730
I wasn't really counting on him anyway.

25:38.730 --> 25:40.270
I just wanted to see if he could spare us

25:40.270 --> 25:41.590
some trouble down the road.

25:41.590 --> 25:42.350
If he fails,

25:42.680 --> 25:43.740
it won't affect us.

26:03.110 --> 26:03.590
Ms. Xia,

26:03.920 --> 26:05.250
should I go check on him?

26:05.960 --> 26:06.480
No need.

26:07.430 --> 26:10.030
There must be something fishy
about this plot.

26:18.750 --> 26:19.280
Grandpa!

26:20.680 --> 26:21.790
Well, Grandpa, open the door!

26:21.790 --> 26:22.320
Grandpa!

26:23.350 --> 26:24.750
What "gold-bearing sand
springing from the ground"?

26:24.750 --> 26:26.640
You were just drunk and seeing things!

26:26.640 --> 26:29.490
Cut the threads of fate...

26:30.270 --> 26:32.100
They said there's gold-bearing sand
in our village.

26:32.100 --> 26:34.240
There can't be any gold-bearing sand here.

26:34.240 --> 26:34.700
Tell me—

26:34.800 --> 26:35.480
isn't it great if we just sell it

26:35.480 --> 26:38.810
and get several hundred thousand
in compensation instead?

26:39.510 --> 26:40.110
If you have the guts,

26:40.110 --> 26:41.310
keep me locked up forever!

26:41.310 --> 26:42.460
Or the day I become the Village Chief,

26:42.460 --> 26:43.160
the first thing I'll do

26:43.160 --> 26:44.760
is sell Stinky Bamboo Ditch!

26:45.160 --> 26:47.490
They can get hundreds of thousands for it!

26:50.160 --> 26:50.620
Ms. Xia!

26:51.800 --> 26:53.110
Turns out that brat, Luo Yaozong,

26:53.110 --> 26:54.580
has been locked up by his grandfather.

26:54.580 --> 26:55.370
His grandfather also claims

26:55.370 --> 26:55.960
that this piece of land

26:55.960 --> 26:57.480
is their family's feng shui treasure site,

26:57.480 --> 26:58.480
called something like

26:58.480 --> 26:59.750
"gold-bearing sand
springing from the ground."

26:59.750 --> 27:00.680
Luo Yaozong was in the house

27:00.680 --> 27:01.350
screaming and shouting,

27:01.350 --> 27:02.400
and all the neighbors heard him.

27:02.400 --> 27:03.440
So this matter

27:03.440 --> 27:04.770
wasn't hard to find out.

27:06.550 --> 27:07.200
If that's

27:07.200 --> 27:08.160
the reason,

27:08.440 --> 27:09.070
it won't affect

27:09.070 --> 27:10.530
our development project.

27:10.960 --> 27:12.440
But will they cause trouble?

27:12.440 --> 27:13.920
Should I make a trip to Ganquan Village?

27:13.920 --> 27:14.380
No need.

27:14.720 --> 27:16.200
Better not to stir things up.

27:16.200 --> 27:17.310
Before the land deal is signed,

27:17.310 --> 27:18.030
none of us should go

27:18.030 --> 27:18.680
to that place again.

27:18.680 --> 27:19.010
Okay.

27:23.920 --> 27:25.850
The hard part isn't buying the land

27:26.160 --> 27:27.790
but getting the apartments sold.

27:27.790 --> 27:29.480
We need a good story.

27:30.920 --> 27:32.510
A treasure  site.

27:33.720 --> 27:36.320
Gold-bearing sand
springing from the ground.

27:37.270 --> 27:38.790
Hasn't the Luo family just handed me

27:38.790 --> 27:40.240
a ready-made story?

27:40.720 --> 27:42.200
Golden Sands Pool.

27:44.830 --> 27:45.160
Okay.

27:45.510 --> 27:47.440
No problem.
I'll go make the arrangements first.

27:47.440 --> 27:47.920
You Li,

27:48.480 --> 27:49.940
how's your mother lately?

27:51.400 --> 27:52.440
Same as before.

27:53.060 --> 27:54.920
The doctor said we need to be patient.

27:54.920 --> 27:56.920
I talk to her every day when I get back.

27:56.920 --> 27:57.800
I believe

27:57.830 --> 27:58.690
she can hear me.

27:59.240 --> 28:00.240
I believe so, too.

28:00.280 --> 28:01.240
If you need anything,

28:01.240 --> 28:02.700
just let the company know.

28:02.960 --> 28:03.880
Thank you, Ms. Xia.

28:03.880 --> 28:04.880
I'll head out now.

28:05.110 --> 28:05.510
Sure.

28:10.280 --> 28:11.240
Hello.

28:11.270 --> 28:12.400
Qihang Real Estate.

28:13.120 --> 28:14.240
Your land acquisition application

28:14.240 --> 28:15.300
has been approved.

28:15.400 --> 28:17.880
Please come by to sign the contract
when you have time.

28:17.880 --> 28:18.880
Great, thank you.

28:18.960 --> 28:20.420
We're available anytime.

28:20.640 --> 28:21.850
I've reviewed the contract.

28:21.850 --> 28:24.600
[Letter of Intent to Lease Land]

28:22.480 --> 28:24.070
It's a standard government template,

28:24.070 --> 28:25.920
with not much flexibility for adjustments.

28:25.920 --> 28:27.680
And the wording is quite strong,

28:27.680 --> 28:28.790
but the framework is solid.

28:28.790 --> 28:30.650
So there shouldn't be any issues.

28:31.070 --> 28:32.350
Ms. Xia, you really take contracts

28:32.350 --> 28:33.310
seriously.

28:34.440 --> 28:36.520
Yes, I have to take it seriously.

28:36.790 --> 28:38.160
Look at the contract you signed!

28:38.160 --> 28:39.160
Look at how the joint liability clauses

28:39.160 --> 28:39.640
are written!

28:39.640 --> 28:40.830
All our company's losses

28:40.830 --> 28:42.290
will be borne by you alone!

28:42.960 --> 28:43.460
Yeah.

28:44.270 --> 28:45.440
When it comes to contracts,

28:45.440 --> 28:47.040
you can never be too careful.

28:47.480 --> 28:48.720
Do you know what's most important

28:48.720 --> 28:50.120
when signing a contract?

28:52.510 --> 28:53.730
The most important thing

28:53.730 --> 28:54.890
is to first verify

28:54.920 --> 28:56.270
if the party you're signing with

28:56.270 --> 28:57.000
is reliable.

28:57.350 --> 28:58.210
Only after that

28:58.310 --> 29:00.680
do you verify
the specific terms and clauses.

29:00.680 --> 29:01.270
The party signing with us this time

29:01.270 --> 29:02.440
is the government—

29:02.510 --> 29:04.110
they won't play word games

29:04.310 --> 29:05.040
or lay traps.

29:05.240 --> 29:06.200
So rest assured.

29:07.680 --> 29:08.480
You're right.

29:08.880 --> 29:11.680
The most important thing is
a reliable other party.

29:11.680 --> 29:13.410
If I had understood this sooner

29:14.070 --> 29:15.270
instead of rushing to

29:15.350 --> 29:17.680
get performance bonuses and a promotion,

29:17.750 --> 29:19.750
maybe I wouldn't have ended up here.

29:19.830 --> 29:20.720
Now,

29:20.920 --> 29:22.610
I don't know
if that's a good thing or not.

29:22.610 --> 29:24.120
[Meeting Room]

29:23.590 --> 29:24.350
This

29:24.350 --> 29:25.660
is the land lease agreement

29:25.660 --> 29:26.920
we discussed earlier.

29:27.440 --> 29:28.160
Take a look.

29:28.510 --> 29:29.560
If everything is in order,

29:29.560 --> 29:30.790
you can sign it.

29:31.720 --> 29:32.110
Okay.

29:35.110 --> 29:37.200
Yuanhui took on all the previous projects,

29:37.200 --> 29:39.000
and Uncle signed the contracts.

29:39.160 --> 29:40.720
This will be the first time

29:41.160 --> 29:42.880
a contract bears Xia Xiaolan's name—

29:42.880 --> 29:44.640
not as a sales representative,

29:45.070 --> 29:45.830
nor as

29:46.110 --> 29:47.750
a project manager,

29:47.960 --> 29:49.200
but entirely as

29:49.450 --> 29:50.690
the sole director

29:50.720 --> 29:52.110
of Qihang Real Estate.

29:56.400 --> 29:56.880
I know

29:58.350 --> 29:59.240
you'll have

29:59.550 --> 30:00.880
an extraordinary life,

30:02.000 --> 30:02.860
and your future

30:03.240 --> 30:04.270
will hold

30:04.270 --> 30:06.270
moments even more brilliant than this one.

30:06.270 --> 30:07.530
Let this accompany you

30:08.550 --> 30:10.750
as you write your brilliant life story.

30:20.580 --> 30:22.680
[Qihang Real Estate Co., Ltd.]

30:25.480 --> 30:26.640
Looks like that letter of intent

30:26.640 --> 30:27.840
was useful after all.

30:27.960 --> 30:28.880
The final price came to

30:28.880 --> 30:29.920
130,000 yuan per mu,

30:29.920 --> 30:31.240
which is lower than I expected.

30:31.240 --> 30:32.240
But the total area

30:32.240 --> 30:33.640
is 23.5 mu.

30:33.830 --> 30:34.590
So the total comes to

30:34.590 --> 30:35.650
3.05 million yuan—

30:35.680 --> 30:37.210
about what we anticipated.

30:38.200 --> 30:39.530
To think that back then,

30:39.680 --> 30:40.480
scraping together

30:40.480 --> 30:42.270
1 million yuan
for Luna's advertising fees

30:42.270 --> 30:43.240
felt nearly impossible.

30:43.240 --> 30:45.200
Now, Xiaolan is acquiring land
for 3 million,

30:45.200 --> 30:46.060
just like that.

30:46.510 --> 30:48.110
You know what feeling I have?

30:48.110 --> 30:50.550
Big money, big swagger.

30:50.880 --> 30:51.680
That doesn't sound like

30:51.680 --> 30:53.480
a compliment, the way you put it.

30:55.750 --> 30:56.240
Xia,

30:57.480 --> 30:59.240
everyone helped out with Luna before.

30:59.240 --> 31:01.240
This time, I contributed the least.

31:01.750 --> 31:02.790
It's mainly because

31:02.790 --> 31:04.590
I just bought a production line,

31:04.900 --> 31:07.030
so there really isn't
that much cash on hand.

31:07.030 --> 31:07.720
On top of that,

31:07.720 --> 31:08.440
Elegance has been chasing after us,

31:08.440 --> 31:10.480
setting up branches one after another.

31:10.480 --> 31:11.340
I had no choice.

31:11.550 --> 31:12.310
So most of the profits

31:12.310 --> 31:13.570
have been reinvested.

31:13.640 --> 31:14.310
Do we know

31:14.310 --> 31:15.590
who's behind Elegance now?

31:15.590 --> 31:16.120
Any idea?

31:16.680 --> 31:18.480
I heard it's a Gangdao merchant.

31:19.270 --> 31:21.070
Ji Ya has definitely backed off.

31:21.240 --> 31:22.750
Well, whoever it is,

31:23.200 --> 31:25.030
they're a competitor either way.

31:25.030 --> 31:25.750
Mainly,

31:25.830 --> 31:27.510
I feel a little guilty that I couldn't

31:27.510 --> 31:29.040
help Qihang more this time.

31:29.350 --> 31:30.110
Chen,

31:30.310 --> 31:31.550
don't think like that.

31:31.550 --> 31:32.270
Consider this

31:32.270 --> 31:33.880
as me personally

31:33.880 --> 31:35.110
borrowing money from you.

31:35.110 --> 31:35.880
Besides,

31:36.000 --> 31:37.350
I know you've had your eye on

31:37.350 --> 31:38.920
that production line
for Luna for a while now.

31:38.920 --> 31:39.790
I can't let my affairs

31:39.790 --> 31:41.190
hold your business back.

31:41.480 --> 31:42.720
On the contrary, doesn't Qihang's

31:42.720 --> 31:43.880
land purchase seem

31:44.070 --> 31:45.200
particularly rash?

31:46.110 --> 31:47.310
Y-You want the truth?

31:49.720 --> 31:51.350
Building houses on a stinking ditch...

31:51.350 --> 31:52.790
Well, I... I think...

31:53.350 --> 31:54.610
What's there to think?

31:54.720 --> 31:55.510
Just trust

31:55.510 --> 31:56.790
Xiaolan, and that's all there is to it.

31:56.790 --> 31:58.310
The building she puts up

31:58.310 --> 31:59.440
will definitely be the best

31:59.440 --> 32:00.300
in Shengcheng.

32:00.920 --> 32:01.240
Yeah.

32:01.240 --> 32:03.070
Xiaolan must've thought it all through!

32:03.070 --> 32:04.070
Right, right, right.

32:04.070 --> 32:04.760
Anyway,

32:04.790 --> 32:06.720
I'm still very grateful to you all!

32:06.920 --> 32:08.680
-Come on, cheers!
-Cheers!

32:12.210 --> 32:13.480
Once the payment is made tomorrow,

32:13.480 --> 32:15.540
all the procedures will be complete.

32:15.570 --> 32:16.370
Next,

32:16.400 --> 32:18.130
it's clearing the site,

32:18.160 --> 32:20.880
surveying, securing loans,
and leveling the foundation.

32:20.880 --> 32:22.280
With so much ahead of you,

32:22.340 --> 32:24.200
I think you'll need an assistant.

32:24.790 --> 32:25.400
Yeah.

32:25.920 --> 32:27.920
I'm thinking of giving Ge Jian a try.

32:28.320 --> 32:29.320
What do you think?

32:31.110 --> 32:32.400
Work at the construction site

32:32.400 --> 32:34.590
mainly involves dealing with workers.

32:34.590 --> 32:36.520
Ge Jian has martial arts training,

32:36.720 --> 32:38.350
so he commands some authority
over the workers.

32:38.350 --> 32:39.160
And after all these years

32:39.160 --> 32:40.000
by your side,

32:40.270 --> 32:41.110
he's picked up a thing or two

32:41.110 --> 32:42.510
about business from you.

32:42.610 --> 32:44.070
He's actually a good choice.

32:44.070 --> 32:44.480
Okay.

32:44.920 --> 32:46.720
Let's give Ge Jian a chance

32:46.750 --> 32:48.350
and see if he's up to the task.

32:50.350 --> 32:52.510
There are still countless things

32:52.790 --> 32:54.400
waiting for me to handle, one by one.

32:54.400 --> 32:56.070
I really wish
the Golden Sands Pool project

32:56.070 --> 32:57.730
could be finished overnight.

32:58.830 --> 33:00.350
It seems our Ms. Xia's work

33:00.480 --> 33:02.640
is never-ending.

33:02.960 --> 33:04.000
Attorney Zhou,

33:04.200 --> 33:05.550
are you complaining

33:05.830 --> 33:07.260
or just wanting more attention?

33:07.260 --> 33:08.150
Neither.

33:08.960 --> 33:09.960
I just feel like

33:10.920 --> 33:13.050
you've been unusually rushed lately,

33:13.440 --> 33:14.550
like you want to

33:14.750 --> 33:16.270
get everything done
as quickly as possible.

33:16.270 --> 33:17.480
You've always had determination

33:17.480 --> 33:18.280
and boldness,

33:18.600 --> 33:20.460
but you didn't like taking risks.

33:24.070 --> 33:24.680
However,

33:25.440 --> 33:26.750
that piece of land is indeed

33:26.750 --> 33:27.590
a rare find.

33:27.920 --> 33:29.450
It would be a pity to miss it.

33:29.510 --> 33:30.000
Ms. Xia,

33:30.720 --> 33:32.150
Qihang's first project

33:32.640 --> 33:34.300
will definitely go smoothly.

33:34.400 --> 33:35.130
You can do it.

33:56.790 --> 33:57.920
Wednesday,

33:58.590 --> 34:00.350
October 9th, 1991.

34:02.510 --> 34:03.570
Qihang Real Estate

34:03.880 --> 34:05.810
purchased its first piece of land.

34:07.200 --> 34:09.060
I hope the project goes smoothly.

34:09.550 --> 34:11.630
I hope there's still time.

34:26.590 --> 34:27.110
Cheng.

34:28.320 --> 34:29.580
Look how happy Xiaolan

34:29.880 --> 34:30.710
was today.

34:31.230 --> 34:32.070
Think back to when

34:32.070 --> 34:33.280
we first met her—

34:33.670 --> 34:35.330
she was still selling duck eggs then.

34:35.330 --> 34:36.000
She wouldn't even

34:36.000 --> 34:37.030
treat herself to a bowl of noodles.

34:37.030 --> 34:37.889
Look at her now—

34:37.960 --> 34:39.360
a real estate developer!

34:41.190 --> 34:41.630
Yeah.

34:42.760 --> 34:44.219
I'm very happy for her too.

34:45.440 --> 34:46.699
I'm just a bit worried—

34:47.440 --> 34:48.900
isn't she being too hasty?

34:49.510 --> 34:51.280
Xiaolan has always been like this.

34:51.280 --> 34:52.550
She seizes the opportunity
the moment she sees one.

34:52.550 --> 34:53.469
She's not afraid of failure.

34:53.469 --> 34:55.190
Failure is no big deal, anyway.

34:55.190 --> 34:56.670
Never look down on the young

34:56.670 --> 34:58.960
just because they're poor
or because they're inexperienced, right?

34:58.960 --> 34:59.710
Besides,

34:59.960 --> 35:01.960
Xiaolan seems to have never failed.

35:02.920 --> 35:03.360
Right.

35:04.000 --> 35:04.510
And even if she did fail,

35:04.510 --> 35:05.960
it wouldn't be the end of the world.

35:05.960 --> 35:06.710
It's not like we're

35:06.710 --> 35:08.510
starting from nothing anymore.

35:08.670 --> 35:10.030
Exactly.

35:10.320 --> 35:10.850
Alright.

35:11.190 --> 35:12.650
I'm going to take a shower.

35:14.710 --> 35:15.440
One day,

35:15.440 --> 35:16.900
when Xiaolan makes it big,

35:17.230 --> 35:18.890
she can build a building here,

35:19.230 --> 35:20.960
and another one there!

35:21.320 --> 35:22.520
They will all be ours!

35:25.030 --> 35:25.560
Awesome!

35:43.150 --> 35:43.550
Hello?

35:43.800 --> 35:45.030
Xiaolan, bad news.

35:45.510 --> 35:46.550
The Chief of Ganquan Village

35:46.550 --> 35:48.000
is causing a scene at Stinky Bamboo Ditch!

35:48.000 --> 35:50.110
This is our Luo family's
feng shui treasure site!

35:50.110 --> 35:51.800
I've guarded it my whole life!

35:52.280 --> 35:53.630
I'm practically one foot in the grave!

35:53.630 --> 35:55.510
And you've swindled it away from me!

35:55.510 --> 35:56.880
You heartless developers!

35:56.880 --> 35:57.960
You are just evil!

35:57.960 --> 35:58.620
Heartless!

35:58.710 --> 35:59.320
You're all heartless!

35:59.320 --> 36:00.230
Mr. Luo!

36:00.230 --> 36:00.630
Swindlers!

36:00.630 --> 36:02.440
We purchased this land legally,

36:02.510 --> 36:03.930
and we have the right to construct here.

36:03.930 --> 36:05.440
The notice is already posted!

36:05.440 --> 36:06.030
Nonsense!

36:06.030 --> 36:06.980
Excuse me! Make way!

36:06.980 --> 36:08.440
It's a government notice!

36:08.670 --> 36:09.370
Director Wang,

36:09.370 --> 36:10.550
what brings you here?

36:10.550 --> 36:12.190
This is my family's
feng shui treasure site!

36:12.190 --> 36:13.390
How could you sell it?

36:13.440 --> 36:14.000
Sir,

36:14.320 --> 36:15.320
please calm down!

36:15.920 --> 36:17.000
Let's get this straight.

36:17.000 --> 36:17.630
This land

36:17.880 --> 36:19.070
belongs to the state,

36:19.070 --> 36:20.550
not your family!

36:21.150 --> 36:22.800
The city is focused on

36:22.960 --> 36:24.690
production and construction!

36:24.800 --> 36:25.440
They went through

36:25.440 --> 36:27.100
the proper approval process!

36:28.440 --> 36:29.040
Come here.

36:32.230 --> 36:33.150
Mr. Luo,

36:33.400 --> 36:34.860
we didn't shortchange you

36:34.960 --> 36:35.630
a single cent

36:35.630 --> 36:37.090
on the land compensation.

36:37.190 --> 36:38.590
Don't get greedy now.

36:39.600 --> 36:41.190
Now, come on, ask them to leave.

36:41.190 --> 36:42.030
Okay, okay.

36:43.670 --> 36:44.070
Dad,

36:44.320 --> 36:45.850
maybe we should go back now.

36:46.290 --> 36:46.710
Well...

36:46.710 --> 36:47.770
Disperse! Go back!

36:47.800 --> 36:48.660
We can't leave!

36:48.920 --> 36:49.960
We won't leave!

36:50.480 --> 36:52.230
It's all because of you, wretched boy—

36:52.230 --> 36:54.150
shouting about our family's feng shui site

36:54.150 --> 36:55.810
until the whole village knew!

36:55.880 --> 36:56.650
I'll teach you a lesson!

36:56.650 --> 36:58.780
Well, what does this have to do with me?

37:01.960 --> 37:03.360
Everyone, go back, go back!

37:03.360 --> 37:03.820
Go back!

37:04.030 --> 37:05.440
Dad, Dad!

37:05.710 --> 37:06.480
Go! Go home!

37:16.960 --> 37:17.420
Senior.

37:17.500 --> 37:18.030
Zhenzhu.

37:19.360 --> 37:20.110
Xiaolan,

37:20.110 --> 37:21.440
what took you so long?

37:21.460 --> 37:23.860
You should've seen what happened just now!

37:23.960 --> 37:24.840
I got here a while ago.

37:24.840 --> 37:26.320
I just went to notify
the subdistrict office.

37:26.320 --> 37:27.510
Rather than handle it myself,

37:27.510 --> 37:29.640
it's better to let them take care of it.

37:29.800 --> 37:31.800
The Luo family will probably
keep coming back.

37:31.800 --> 37:32.550
With the subdistrict office in charge,

37:32.550 --> 37:34.280
they won't dare cause trouble.

37:34.280 --> 37:34.670
Okay.

37:55.920 --> 37:57.320
We can't just let this go.

37:58.230 --> 37:59.360
I've already given my word to

37:59.360 --> 38:01.030
the officials
from the Futian Subdistrict Office.

38:01.030 --> 38:03.070
Please don't go causing trouble again.

38:03.070 --> 38:03.920
Otherwise, I won't be able to keep

38:03.920 --> 38:05.440
my position as Chief here!

38:06.400 --> 38:07.550
You're afraid of losing your post,

38:07.550 --> 38:08.320
but I'm not!

38:15.480 --> 38:15.880
Get up!

38:16.280 --> 38:17.340
Go boil some water!

38:18.960 --> 38:20.420
How can you just sit there?

38:24.510 --> 38:26.110
This location is quite nice.

38:26.920 --> 38:27.510
Xiaolan,

38:28.770 --> 38:30.420
you hid it really well.

38:32.110 --> 38:33.000
Mr. Mao,

38:33.070 --> 38:35.030
I truly wasn't trying to keep it from you.

38:35.030 --> 38:37.450
It's just that you
attract too much attention.

38:37.450 --> 38:38.670
I didn't even dare come here often myself—

38:38.670 --> 38:40.280
afraid someone might swoop in and take it.

38:40.280 --> 38:41.710
Other developers aside,

38:41.960 --> 38:43.840
if the Luo family
had caught wind of it early on,

38:43.840 --> 38:45.800
getting this land
would have been touch-and-go.

38:45.800 --> 38:47.130
Better safe than sorry.

38:51.230 --> 38:52.840
The water here is flowing.

38:53.320 --> 38:55.320
Once you clear away all this debris,

38:55.480 --> 38:57.760
the condition of the land
will be much clearer.

38:57.760 --> 38:59.590
The name of this place is awful, though—

38:59.590 --> 39:00.790
Stinky Bamboo Ditch.

39:01.000 --> 39:02.630
We have to change it.

39:03.070 --> 39:03.930
Of course we do.

39:04.000 --> 39:04.590
Stinky Bamboo Ditch

39:04.590 --> 39:06.400
is just what the local villagers call it.

39:06.400 --> 39:07.710
I plan to rename it

39:07.880 --> 39:08.940
Golden Sands Pool.

39:09.490 --> 39:10.200
Rumor has it

39:10.230 --> 39:12.230
that gold-bearing sand
springs from the water here.

39:12.230 --> 39:13.320
Whether that's true or not,

39:13.320 --> 39:14.720
it's an auspicious name.

39:15.600 --> 39:16.880
There's flowing water
and gold-bearing sand.

39:16.880 --> 39:18.100
Gold mines are rare,

39:18.360 --> 39:19.960
but traces of gold in sand...

39:20.440 --> 39:21.100
are common.

39:22.030 --> 39:23.280
I just want to build houses.

39:23.280 --> 39:25.280
I'm not looking to dig up a gold mine.

39:26.030 --> 39:27.840
Are gold in the sand and gold mines

39:27.840 --> 39:29.190
the same thing?

39:29.440 --> 39:30.670
Stop dreaming!

39:30.960 --> 39:32.800
Sand often contains tiny traces of gold,

39:32.800 --> 39:34.190
but most of it

39:34.190 --> 39:35.320
isn't worth mining.

39:35.630 --> 39:37.320
For that legend to hold true,

39:37.760 --> 39:40.880
the sand would need to contain
an unusually high amount of gold.

39:40.880 --> 39:41.400
Look.

39:41.920 --> 39:44.760
These shiny bits are mica fragments,

39:44.920 --> 39:46.400
not gold in the sand.

39:49.440 --> 39:50.510
In that case,

39:50.960 --> 39:52.880
we need to tell the legend

39:53.590 --> 39:54.280
of the gold-bearing sand

39:54.280 --> 39:55.940
as dramatically as possible.

39:56.710 --> 39:57.360
Ms. Xia,

39:57.710 --> 39:58.840
I've already sent

39:58.840 --> 39:59.630
the advertorials about Golden Sands Pool

39:59.630 --> 40:00.880
and the photos of the Luo family

40:00.880 --> 40:01.510
causing trouble last time

40:01.510 --> 40:03.280
to various media outlets in Yuesheng.

40:03.280 --> 40:04.280
But...

40:06.030 --> 40:06.960
It's okay. Go on.

40:07.920 --> 40:08.920
Several editors

40:08.920 --> 40:09.710
knew about the land's

40:09.710 --> 40:10.840
original condition

40:11.190 --> 40:12.920
and thought the story
would have no impact.

40:12.920 --> 40:14.380
Some even told me outright

40:14.740 --> 40:15.880
that the content was too far-fetched

40:15.880 --> 40:16.510
for serious media outlets

40:16.510 --> 40:17.910
to run that kind of story.

40:18.360 --> 40:19.360
Not necessarily.

40:19.760 --> 40:20.230
Ms. Xia.

40:21.150 --> 40:21.810
Manager Ge.

40:21.840 --> 40:22.240
You Li.

40:22.280 --> 40:23.230
I'll be going now.

40:23.230 --> 40:23.630
Okay.

40:24.110 --> 40:24.480
Okay.

40:32.430 --> 40:32.890
Ms. Xia,

40:33.480 --> 40:34.510
everything you asked for

40:34.510 --> 40:35.070
is ready.

40:36.590 --> 40:37.050
Ge Jian,

40:37.440 --> 40:38.770
come take a look at this.

40:48.050 --> 40:50.800
Gold-bearing sand
springing from the ground is no legend

40:50.800 --> 40:53.230
but rather something
we've seen with our own eyes.

40:53.230 --> 40:56.630
So, this is the gold-bearing sand
springing from the ground.

40:57.770 --> 40:59.040
[Golden Sands Pool
Construction Project Office]

41:14.710 --> 41:15.550
Be careful!

41:16.760 --> 41:17.190
Okay!

41:24.550 --> 41:25.300
What's going on?

41:25.300 --> 41:25.930
Watch out!

41:25.960 --> 41:26.320
Okay!

41:26.360 --> 41:26.840
Ms. Xia,

41:27.590 --> 41:29.790
we've started the silt-clearing work.

41:30.840 --> 41:32.370
I wonder if this is the sight

41:32.470 --> 41:33.190
Luo Yaozong's grandfather witnessed

41:33.190 --> 41:34.190
back in the day.

41:46.000 --> 41:46.570
Boss!

41:47.150 --> 41:48.750
Looks like we've found gold!

41:50.400 --> 41:51.000
Boss, look.

41:51.000 --> 41:51.570
There's gold!

41:51.570 --> 41:52.050
Gold!

41:54.890 --> 41:55.550
Get back to work.

41:55.550 --> 41:56.000
Okay.

42:08.760 --> 42:09.490
Dig! Faster!

42:10.610 --> 42:11.590
Look, is this it?

42:17.110 --> 42:17.570
Ms. Xia.

42:23.400 --> 42:24.150
Stay here and keep an eye on things.

42:24.150 --> 42:26.210
I'm going to tell my grandpa! Come on!

42:34.320 --> 42:35.650
Quick, call the police.

42:40.070 --> 42:41.070
Dig faster! There really is gold!

42:41.070 --> 42:42.510
There really is!

42:51.510 --> 42:52.070
Grandpa!

42:52.840 --> 42:53.370
Grandpa!

42:53.800 --> 42:55.330
They dug out gold, Grandpa!

42:55.510 --> 42:56.040
Grandpa!

42:57.280 --> 42:58.210
They dug up gold!

42:58.760 --> 42:59.190
That... That...

42:59.190 --> 43:00.550
That land really yielded gold!

43:00.550 --> 43:00.960
Quick!

43:01.440 --> 43:02.030
Get everyone!

43:02.030 --> 43:02.760
Let's go, let's go!

43:02.760 --> 43:04.200
Our family's feng shui treasure site—

43:04.200 --> 43:04.960
we must get it back!

43:04.960 --> 43:05.800
Let's go! Go!
